          },
          {
            "id": "2",
            "icon": "architecture",
            "title": "Tu Misión",
            "content": "Diseñar: 1) Network topology (DMZ, VLANs, segmentation). 2) Firewall rules y policies. 3) Remote access solution. 4) Monitoring strategy. 5) Incident response plan.",
            "insight": "No existe 'perfect' architecture, solo trade-offs. Defense in depth es key."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
